headline: Euronet's Q4 Earnings Beat on EFT Segment Strength, '25 EPS View Up
summary: EEFT's Q4 results benefit from strength in its three segments, attributable to higher transactions. It currently expects 2025 adjusted EPS to witness 12-16% year-over-year growth.
